         AUTHENTICATION FRONTEND DEMO
This is a frontend demo for an authentication system project. It includes multi-page navigation with Home, Login, Register, and Dashboard pages.
           FEATURES
- Home Page: Landing page with navigation links
- Login Page: Demo login from (frontend only)
- Register Page: Demo registration form (frontend only)
- Dashboard Page: Demo dashboard page
- Navigation: Easy link-based navigation between pages
- Styling: Basic CSS applied for clean layout
         NOTES
- This is frontend only, the backend runs locally with Node.js and MongoDB.
- This project demonstrate multi-page site structure, navigate, and CSS styling.
         LIVE DEMO
- check it out here:
